channel.title: Wasted Inc 317 , 474 game frame
channel.description:
I started this project 4months ago and I'm 70% done. Iv done a lot of things, that i will name later, so far it needs some fixes but it's playable so far ;D [center]----------------------------------------------------------- Details: All skills working. It's different from any other server. Based more on skilling. Draynor as home town. Reasonable custom items(those that would suit dark medieval ages) Experience lamps (custom made) Skiller shop (custom made, custom interface) God sword stances, walking, attacking, blocking, running Item forging, that includes god swords, spirit shields, dragon fire shield etc. Fixed usable doors in home and other used citys Custom PvP drops. Increased boss hit ratio and damage ( increase value of drops) Added Shiny keys (when used on chest at home you get a random item) Most of the skill places transferred to home and fishing colony ----------------------------------------------------------- And still working on many things.
Ill update this as soon as ill add more things. ----------------------------------------------------------- Pictures: Home: [img]http://img6.imageshack.us/img6/3034/0010k.png[/img] [img]http://img156.imageshack.us/img156/5696/0017.png[/img] ----------------------------------------------------------- Custom Skill places: Thieving. [img]http://img37.imageshack.us/img37/1531/0006p.png[/img] Smithing. [img]http://img148.imageshack.us/img148/1283/0008a.png[/img] Mining. [img]http://img413.imageshack.us/img413/3430/0009.png[/img] Custom items: [img]http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/2449/0000h.png[/img] [img]http://img155.imageshack.us/img155/7131/0001d.png[/img] [img]http://img32.imageshack.us/img32/7793/0002ya.png[/img] ----------------------------------------------------------- Custom interfaces: Skill shop. [img]http://img404.imageshack.us/img404/6025/0003p.png[/img] Experience lamps. [img]http://img28.imageshack.us/img28/1453/0004cg.png[/img] Boss teleport menu. [img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/5403/0005kh.png[/img] ----------------------------------------------------------- Bosses: King black dragon. [img]http://img18.imageshack.us/img18/9837/0007q.png[/img] Chaos elemental. [img]http://img219.imageshack.us/img219/2296/0011i.png[/img] New bandos lair. [img]http://img132.imageshack.us/img132/9914/0012y.png[/img] Bandos boss. [img]http://img532.imageshack.us/img532/386/0014.png[/img] Kalphite queen. [img]http://img35.imageshack.us/img35/7960/0015e.png[/img] ----------------------------------------------------------- Still to come: Increased skill experience rate. Fix all drops(including random drops from chest, rewards etc). Fix range damage, wielding. Add proper equipment stats to equip. Add more items to pest control and assault. Increase other NPC damage. Made bosses harder, yet possible to defeat. Add more special creeps. Upcoming 3 new quests. Fix minor bugs with character saving problems. Work on economy. Add guide for new comers. Add skill tabs. Fix item stats. More coming soon. ----------------------------------------------------------- [/center]
More pictures coming soon ;D Do post suggestions, criticism and other, if you did drop by to check on this server, please do post how it looks, it takes several seconds.
